If I'd been thirsty, and if I had coffee,

528
01:07:22,830 --> 01:07:25,526
I'd have held the coins by the edge.

529
01:07:27,401 --> 01:07:32,771
You're on a Polaroid I took
at the gas station!

530
01:07:33,140 --> 01:07:34,266
That's a lie.

531
01:07:34,308 --> 01:07:37,709
You would have recognized me at
the café in Nîmes. I was there.

532
01:07:41,248 --> 01:07:43,512
Second table on the right.

533
01:07:47,855 --> 01:07:48,822
Passport.

534
01:08:05,186 --> 01:08:08,622
I've thought a lot about
our meeting, Mr. Hofman.

535
01:08:08,689 --> 01:08:11,715
Since the beginning,
I felt the need to see you.

536
01:08:11,826 --> 01:08:14,090
When you left the café,

537
01:08:14,128 --> 01:08:16,221
I realized I couldn't wait any longer.

538
01:08:17,732 --> 01:08:20,223
What you said on television pursuaded me.

539
01:08:20,268 --> 01:08:22,998
I gathered the courage you spoke of.

540
01:08:25,273 --> 01:08:27,207
You can kill me.

541
01:08:28,409 --> 01:08:30,502
I acknowledge your right to do so.

542
01:08:30,544 --> 01:08:31,909
I'll take the risk.

543
01:08:33,881 --> 01:08:36,873
But I'm banking on your curiosity.

544
01:08:37,652 --> 01:08:40,815
You want to know what
happened to Miss Saskia.

545
01:08:58,839 --> 01:09:01,535
When I was 1 6,
I discovered something.

546
01:10:05,706 --> 01:10:08,573
Everyone has those thoughts,
but no one ever jumps.

547
01:10:10,144 --> 01:10:12,874
I told myself:
"Imagine you're jumping."

548
01:10:14,281 --> 01:10:16,806
Is it predestined that I won't jump?

549
01:10:17,651 --> 01:10:19,983
How can it be predestined
that I won't?

550
01:10:21,222 --> 01:10:23,747
So, to go against what is
predestined, one must jump.

551
01:10:23,891 --> 01:10:24,880
I jumped.

552
01:10:27,695 --> 01:10:29,162
The fall was a holy event.

553
01:10:29,196 --> 01:10:33,326
I broke my left arm and lost 2 fingers.
Why did I jump?

554
01:10:33,467 --> 01:10:35,799
A slight abnormality in my personality,

555
01:10:36,170 --> 01:10:38,365
imperceptible to those around me.

556
01:10:38,472 --> 01:10:41,498
You can find me listed
in the medical encyclopedias

557
01:10:41,542 --> 01:10:44,534
under "Sociopath" in the new editions.

558
01:10:44,578 --> 01:10:46,546
Did you rape Saskia?

559
01:10:47,381 --> 01:10:48,473
Come now, Mr. Hofman!

560
01:10:51,719 --> 01:10:55,416
