experience came to mind.

561
01:10:55,656 --> 01:10:56,816
First place!

562
01:10:58,492 --> 01:11:00,426
Denise! I thought so.

563
01:11:00,528 --> 01:11:02,621
A bit to the left. There.

564
01:11:03,264 --> 01:11:04,595
To the left.

565
01:11:04,632 --> 01:11:06,361
