684
01:24:47,446 --> 01:24:49,573
Excuse me, miss.

685
01:24:49,782 --> 01:24:51,545
- Do you speak French?
- Of course.

686
01:24:52,818 --> 01:24:54,445
Could you help me?

687
01:24:54,620 --> 01:24:57,783
