688
01:24:58,357 --> 01:24:59,119
My car!

689
01:24:59,692 --> 01:25:01,660
Where's the trailer?

690
01:25:02,027 --> 01:25:04,689
Over there. I'll bring the car.

691
01:25:05,464 --> 01:25:08,262
