01:34:40,154 --> 01:34:43,646
After, you'll experience
exactly what she did.

771
01:34:47,762 --> 01:34:52,131
If she's dead,
I'm also going to die.

772
01:34:53,935 --> 01:34:54,924
You're crazy.

773
01:34:57,138 --> 01:34:58,867
It's the only way.

774
01:35:00,675 --> 01:35:02,609
You can't be serious!

775
01:35:04,012 --> 01:35:06,480
I don't want to punish you.

776
01:35:06,514 --> 01:35:07,708
I'm not saying another word.

777
01:35:08,516 --> 01:35:09,983
I don't care about you.

778
01:35:10,885 --> 01:35:14,048
All I want to know is
what happened to her.

779
01:35:14,222 --> 01:35:15,849
I understand, Mr. Hofman.

780
01:35:15,890 --> 01:35:17,881
I've put myself in your shoes.

781
01:35:18,593 --> 01:35:21,892
In fact, I believe that you
don't want to punish me.

782
01:35:22,196 --> 01:35:25,563
But I'm not so certain I should.
Understand?

783
01:35:25,934 --> 01:35:29,802
I believe you,
but I must pretend that I don't.

784
01:35:32,240 --> 01:35:33,434
So, drink.

785
01:35:34,876 --> 01:35:37,106
It's truly the only way.

786
01:35:39,881 --> 01:35:41,041
What's in it?

787
01:35:41,849 --> 01:35:45,546
I've already told you:
a sleeping pill dissolved in coffee.

788
01:35:55,763 --> 01:35:58,960
The car keys.
I'd love to look at them one more time.

789
01:36:07,642 --> 01:36:11,942
Mr. Hofman, understand once
and for all:

790
01:36:14,082 --> 01:36:16,277
what use are these keys to you?

791
01:36:17,218 --> 01:36:18,480
You're powerless.

792
01:36:18,620 --> 01:36:19,644
You're bluffing!

793
01:36:20,521 --> 01:36:23,649
Assume you're right.
Can you be absolutely sure?

794
01:36:24,926 --> 01:36:26,860
That's where your problem lies.

795
01:36:29,397 --> 01:36:33,663
You must keep in mind the possibility
that there's no proof against me.

796
01:36:34,002 --> 01:36:36,334
That could spoil all your chances.

797
01:36:36,604 --> 01:36:40,472
Mr. Hofman, I've been analyzing
what goes in your head for the last 3 years.

798
01:36:40,508 --> 01:36:43,477
You can leave.
Even go to the police with the keys.

799
01:36:43,511 --> 01:36:48,039
But then, you'll never know
what happened to Miss Saskia.

800
01:36:49,283 --> 01:36:53,686
On the other hand, drink...
and you'll know.

801
01:36:54,322 --> 01:36:56,688
In less than 1 hour, I guarantee you.

802
01:36:58,893 --> 01:37:00,121
I know all I need to know.

803
01:37:00,762 --> 01:37:03,788
I don't care about the rest.
I'm leaving.

804
01:37:08,770 --> 01:37:10,362
And the uncertainty?

805
01:37:11,105 --> 01:37:13,835
The eternal uncertainty,
Mr. Hofman?

806
01:37:14,108 --> 01:37:15,871
That's the worst.

807
01:37:18,579 --> 01:37:20,638
I wanted to help you out!

808
01:39:26,300 --> 01:39:27,062
So?

809
01:39:30,872 --> 01:39:35,332
I told myself:
"Imagine you're drinking."

810
01:39:36,077 --> 01:39:40,309
Where is it predestined
I won't drink?

811
01:39:40,615 --> 01:39:45,484
So, to go against what is
predestined, I must drink.

812
01:39:47,421 --> 01:39:49,582
It takes 1 0 minutes to work.

813
01:39:52,627 --> 01:39:54,822
I drank it for her!

814
01:39:56,430 --> 01:40:01,424
Sure! She never left you the time
to fall out of love!

815
01:40:42,543 --> 01:40:46,570
Help! Help!

816
01:41:01,028 --> 01:41:03,360
Help!

817
01:41:20,314 --> 01:41:22,839
Oh no, it can't be!

818
01:42:07,862 --> 01:42:11,992
My name is Rex Hofman
and that's a bit weird...

819
01:42:15,169 --> 01:42:21,404
Rex Hofman... Rex Hof...

820
01:42:57,478 --> 01:42:58,775
Saskia!

821
01:43:07,455 --> 01:43:08,752
Saskia!

822
01:44:32,273 --> 01:44:35,902
MYSTERIOUS DOUBLE
DISAPPEARANCE

823
01:44:36,043 --> 01:44:43,176
AFTER SASKIA WAGTER
HER FRIEND REX HOFMAN...

